//  test_latent_ode.hexa — Latent ODE / Neural CDE (#260) tests
//
//  Verifies:
//    1. Linear field output length
//    2. Euler constant-decay exact limit
//    3. Euler vs RK4 accuracy on linear ODE
//    4. Encoder output shape
//    5. Decoder output shape
//    6. End-to-end forward shape
//    7. Linear interp at endpoints
//    8. Linear interp at midpoint
//    9. Linear interp clamping outside range
